entry.defn: slash, bend Alt.: 乀 乁

It does not occur as a character on its own. In combination, it historically takes meanings such as "open mouth", "box", "frame", "hole" or "receptacle".
As for the similar radicals 匚 and 冂, the name of radical 17 is purely descriptive of its shape
child, seed Alt.: 孑 孒 孓
door, house Alt.: 户 戸
Dropper, 市斗, sometimes represented by 斗 alone, is also the symbol for a Chinese traditional measurement of dry volume equaling about 10 liters.
negative, no, not Alt.: 无 旡
death, decay Alt.: 歹 歺
mother, do not Alt.: 毋 毌
half of tree trunk, split wood Alt.: 丬
rice paddy, field Alt.: 由 甲 申 甴 电
ancestor, veneration. Represents an altar or offering table. Alt.: 礻
cover, west Alt.: 西 覀
long, grow Alt.: 镸 长
even, uniformly Alt.: 斉 齐
meaning as an independent word is unknown, but is often interpreted to be a "lid" when used as a radical
